## Call graph (open hero screen)

1. Adv-map / town code → **`0x00432D30`** (main open) or **`0x007E1E40`** (debug/arena path).
2. **`0x00AF7520`** factory builds `CHeroScreen2`.
3. Primary vtable **`+0x04`** binds hero; **`+0x2C`** initializes; **`+0x10C`/`+0x114`** set merged/split layout.
4. Parent shell (`0x007A9E60` embeds screen @ `[parent+0x14]`) calls **`+0x80`** for tab index.
5. Shell refresh **`0x006CA4E0`** resolves panes via MI **`+0x94`**, then **`0x006CA280`** builds `"Skills"` / `"Biography"` / `"Inventory"` layout (DLL patch region).

